divs: Sighting DetailsWITNESS WAS OUTSIDE OF MATT BLATT CAR DEALERS IN VINELAND WHEN THEY LOOKED UP AND SAW APROX 50 CRESCENT SHAPED OBJECTS IN THE SKY. THEY WERE THE SIZE OF AN ASPRIN HELD AT ARMS LENGTH. THE OBJECTS CAME IN WAVES ,.SHAPED LIKE A BOOMERANG. THEY DID MANUVER INTO DIFFERENT FORMATIONS. THEY WERE IN THE SOUTH EAST SKY. THEY WERE VERY HIGH AND A SHINY SILVER OR WHITE SURFACE , DEPENDIND ON THE SUNS REFLECTIONS. THE OBJECTS THEN FLEW OUT OF SIGHT. THE ONLY AIRPORT CLOSE BY WOULD BE MILLVILLE AIRPORT. APROX 10 MILES.
